Package: cibmtrrepro
Title: Canonical CIBMTR Endpoint and Model Implementations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dhriti", "Sood", email = "dhriti05sood@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Unit-tested implementations of the standard CIBMTR survival and competing-risk
    endpoints (OS/DFS/PFS/GRFS via Kaplan-Meier + Cox; relapse/NRM/GVHD/engraftment via
    cumulative incidence + Gray + Fine-Gray or cause-specific Cox). The reproduction panel's
    Analyst agent calls these functions so every study shares one validated statistical core.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    survival,
    cmprsk
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    tidycmprsk,
    arrow,
    IPDfromKM
Config/testthat/edition: 3
